293
00:14:19,029 --> 00:14:20,745
(keyboard clicking)

294
00:14:20,769 --> 00:14:21,579
[Daitetsu] Did you get the data yet?

295
00:14:21,603 --> 00:14:22,686
I need more time.

296
00:14:22,710 --> 00:14:25,758
