I think it's the, a riddle.

302
00:14:40,060 --> 00:14:40,990
What's going on?

303
00:14:41,014 --> 00:14:43,133
What the hell is up with this guy?

304
00:14:43,157 --> 00:14:45,780
You guys can work on
the riddle if you like,

305
00:14:45,804 --> 00:14:49,196
