306
00:14:49,220 --> 00:14:50,570
- Got ya.
- You all right?

307
00:14:51,860 --> 00:14:53,576
Darling, please wake up.

308
00:14:53,600 --> 00:14:54,656
What's wrong?

309
00:14:54,680 --> 00:14:56,046
This heat's too much.

310
00:14:56,070 --> 00:14:58,423
Quick, one of you go
and get me a cold towel.

311
00:15:00,250 --> 00:15:01,646
[Ryoko] How's she doing?

312
00:15:01,670 --> 00:15:03,348
She's not looking so good.

313
00:15:03,372 --> 00:15:06,176
We need to get her out of
here as soon as possible.

314
00:15:06,200 --> 00:15:07,676
I see.

315
00:15:07,700 --> 00:15:08,617
What's the plan?

316
00:15:08,641 --> 00:15:09,646
I'll think of something.

317
00:15:09,670 --> 00:15:10,853
Just give me a minute.

318
00:15:14,450 --> 00:15:16,626
I'm afraid we may have no choice,

319
00:15:16,650 --> 00:15:18,176
but to leave this one to fate.

320
00:15:18,200 --> 00:15:19,646
We have no plan, Koume,

321
00:15:19,670 --> 00:15:21,463
so it just might come to that.

322
00:15:23,190 --> 00:15:24,936
[Koume] If this were a public bath,

323
00:15:24,960 --> 00:15:26,616
