324
00:15:26,640 --> 00:15:28,126
Add cold water.

325
00:15:28,150 --> 00:15:29,696
Yeah, that's the easiest way

326
00:15:29,720 --> 00:15:31,040
to bring down the temperature.

327
00:15:31,064 --> 00:15:34,526
Why didn't I think
of that earlier, Koume?

328
00:15:34,550 --> 00:15:38,628
I'll stop the hot water
and let in some cold.

329
00:15:38,652 --> 00:15:41,305
(gunshots ringing)

330
00:15:41,329 --> 00:15:42,776
(bamboo rustling)

331
00:15:42,800 --> 00:15:44,706
Just don't miss, okay?

332
00:15:44,730 --> 00:15:46,204
I'll do my best.

333
00:15:46,228 --> 00:15:49,440
(gunshots ringing)

334
00:15:49,464 --> 00:15:52,297
(water splashing)

335
00:15:53,860 --> 00:15:55,356
Okay Koume, ready?

336
00:15:55,380 --> 00:15:58,386
Just hurry, the water's
freezing over here.

337
00:15:58,410 --> 00:15:59,660
[Ryoko] Ready, set, go.

338
00:16:02,853 --> 00:16:05,686
(water splashing)

339
00:16:08,524 --> 00:16:10,304
[Woman] Let's move
her near the cold water.

340
00:16:10,328 --> 00:16:11,328
All right.

341
00:16:13,955 --> 00:16:15,953
I got it, a square wheel.

342
00:16:15,977 --> 00:16:17,656
And that's because?

343
00:16:17,680 --> 00:16:19,836
I don't know, I just thought so.

344
00:16:19,860 --> 00:16:22,916
You idiot, you can't just give an answer

345
00:16:22,940 --> 00:16:24,986
