348
00:16:29,170 --> 00:16:31,256
That makes just as much sense.

349
00:16:31,280 --> 00:16:33,917
I don't need any of
your lip, you got it?

350
00:16:33,941 --> 00:16:35,979
Don't you give me that face

351
00:16:36,003 --> 00:16:38,146
and don't you even test me.

352
00:16:38,170 --> 00:16:39,636
Will you two stop?

