00:16:58,980 --> 00:17:00,475
It was nothing.

363
00:17:00,499 --> 00:17:02,624
I can't tell anymore.

364
00:17:02,648 --> 00:17:04,652
I'll have to get Koume.

365
00:17:04,676 --> 00:17:08,066
Koume, Koume, where are you?

366
00:17:08,090 --> 00:17:09,766
I'll call you back.

367
00:17:09,790 --> 00:17:13,083
Koume, why are you changing now?

368
00:17:14,060 --> 00:17:16,173
I have a hunch.

369
00:17:17,820 --> 00:17:20,156
That bomb is set by remote.

370
00:17:20,180 --> 00:17:21,893
They can't be far.

371
00:17:23,230 --> 00:17:24,993
Not up here in the mountains.

372
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:27,343
Too much interference.

373
00:17:28,480 --> 00:17:31,003
Where would you even begin to look?

374
00:17:32,930 --> 00:17:34,396
There's an old abandoned cottage

375
00:17:34,420 --> 00:17:36,456
about a 10 minutes' drive from here

376
00:17:36,480 --> 00:17:39,703
so I thought I'd just go and clean it out.

