436
00:21:06,100 --> 00:21:07,633
Her and her big gun.

437
00:21:12,713 --> 00:21:14,306
[Ryoko] Hello?

438
00:21:14,330 --> 00:21:16,356
It's me, I screwed up.

439
00:21:16,380 --> 00:21:17,204
