00:22:58,444 --> 00:22:59,714
I finally got through.

475
00:22:59,738 --> 00:23:01,978
Who were you talking to for so long?

476
00:23:02,002 --> 00:23:03,711
We don't have time for all this.

477
00:23:03,735 --> 00:23:08,076
